card.name: CW - CCW376 - Data Extract Experian issue

data.text:
@neilbosworth @gillianoberholzer @willemhuman 

I have been looking into it and couldn't find anything wrong with the data and code.

This morning i noticed that the Experian Extract has a piece of code commented out which checks for exist records.
I cant remember when we made this change or why we made it.

But in essence it allows an existing record to be sent out.
Not sure why this change was made.

We will have to check through logs or i can just put the code back in for now.
